aa(lp99
VWhat's the process that's having the same effect
p100
aVin cultural evolution
p101
aVas sex is having in biological evolution?
p102
aVAnd I think the answer is exchange,
p103
aVthe habit of exchanging one thing for another.
p104
aVIt's a unique human feature.
p105
aVNo other animal does it.
p106
aVYou can teach them in the laboratory to do a little bit of exchange \u2014
p107
aVand indeed there's reciprocity in other animals \u2014
p108
aVBut the exchange of one object for another never happens.
p109
aVAs Adam Smith said, "No man ever saw a dog
p110
aVmake a fair exchange of a bone with another dog."
p111
aV(Laughter)
