aa(lp153
VAsk yourself how long you would have to work
p154
aVto provide for yourself
p155
aVan hour of reading light this evening to read a book by.
p156
aVIf you had to start from scratch, let's say you go out into the countryside.
p157
aVYou find a sheep. You kill it. You get the fat out of it.
p158
aVYou render it down. You make a candle, etc. etc.
p159
aVHow long is it going to take you? Quite a long time.
p160
aVHow long do you actually have to work
p161
aVto earn an hour of reading light
p162
aVif you're on the average wage in Britain today?
p163
