p164
aVBack in 1950,
p165
aVyou would have had to work for eight seconds on the average wage
p166
aVto acquire that much light.
p167
aVAnd that's seven and a half seconds of prosperity that you've gained
p168
aVsince 1950, as it were,
p169
aVbecause that's seven and a half seconds in which you can do something else,
p170
aVor you can acquire another good or service.
