aVBut I've got no evidence for that.
p239
aVIt just looks like the first thing we did
p240
aVwas work male for female and female for male.
p241
aVIn all hunter-gatherer societies today,
p242
aVthere's a foraging division of labor
p243
aVbetween, on the whole, hunting males and gathering females.
p244
aVIt isn't always quite that simple,
p245
aVbut there's a distinction between
p246
aVspecialized roles for males and females.
